# Project core

- **Stack:** Swift 5.9+ / SPM, macOS 13+, Apple Silicon first. Repo: `gurkanfikretgunak/masterfabric-mac-cli`.
- **Products:** `mf` (CLI + MCP), `MasterFabricMenuBar`, shared `MasterFabricCore`. Keep logic in Core; thin CLI/UI shells.
- **Privacy:** Sensors and `config.toml` stay on the Mac. No analytics/telemetry. MCP is **local stdio only**.
- **Version:** Root `VERSION` is source of truth. After edits run `make version-sync`. Keep `Formula/masterfabric.rb` tag in sync on release.
- **Language:** Code comments, commits, PR titles/bodies in **English**. Chat may be Turkish.
- **Docs:** User-facing install/MCP examples live in `README.md` and `examples/`. Prefer updating those over inventing new doc files unless asked.

```text
✅ Metrics/services → MasterFabricCore
❌ Duplicate SMC/battery logic inside mf or MenuBar targets
```
